ors include orange, apple, lemon-lime, strawberry and lime, and red berry.</p><p>To learn more, or to try out SiS’s new line for yourself, go to the product <a href=\"https://www.scienceinsport.com/betafuel\">page</a> on SiS’s website.</p><p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/14131007/beta-bundle-1.jpg\" alt=\"sis beta fuel\" width=\"614\" height=\"650\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/14131007/beta-bundle-1.jpg 614w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/14131007/beta-bundle-1-283x300.jpg 283w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/14131007/beta-bundle-1-113x120.jpg 113w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/14131007/beta-bundle-1-397x420.jpg 397w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 614px) 100vw, 614px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb25 src ng ngcb25 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/14131007/beta-bundle-1.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/14131007/beta-bundle-1.jpg 614w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/14131007/beta-bundle-1-283x300.jpg 283w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/14131007/beta-bundle-1-113x120.jpg 113w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/14131007/beta-bundle-1-397x420.jpg 397w\"></p></div></div>","author":"Sam Anderson","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"33a2c7858c8ca1a5ac7492cf5764c3411673114c5129d157f8079dc5c9340733","category":"Cycling"}